Description: A native Linux desktop client for Ollama
 ORooster is a native Linux desktop client for Ollama. It provides a clean,
 fast chat interface to interact with locally-running LLMs — no browser required.
 .
 Unlike web-based UIs, ORooster runs as a lightweight native app (~13 MB) with
 system tray integration, streaming responses, and automatic dark/light theme support.
 .
 Features:
  - Streaming chat with real-time token-by-token response rendering
  - Model selector to switch between installed Ollama models
  - Markdown rendering with code blocks and syntax highlighting
  - System tray integration with minimize to tray functionality
  - Dark/light theme that follows system preference automatically
  - Connection status indicator showing Ollama daemon status
